  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2230770/extras/4674caba443f01807c043c1945458735.avif?t=1726618775\" width=610 height=150 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Survive</h2>With different character classes, weapons, and companions, you must battle your way through various alien planets in an attempt to reach the final boss and win. Collect gems along the way to select new skills and upgrade your character.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2230770/extras/5b1f5620eff9d6c8a92d1dbd0d40549a.poster.avif?t=1726618775\" width=609 height=196 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2230770/extras/5b1f5620eff9d6c8a92d1dbd0d40549a.webm?t=1726618775\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Bosses</h2>Survive until the end of each stage and encounter the final Boss. <br>With an ever-changing set of skills, powers, and abilities, players must combine their efforts to take down the end-level Boss.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2230770/extras/a175c16e5559eaedddb1aec6c69dee9b.poster.avif?t=1726618775\" width=608 height=190 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2230770/extras/a175c16e5559eaedddb1aec6c69dee9b.webm?t=1726618775\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2230770/extras/a175c16e5559eaedddb1aec6c69dee9b.mp4?t=1726618775\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Ultimate Skills</h2>In addition to common skills, each character has unique skills and ultimate powers. You can combine these skills with common ones and build new, more powerful skills. Can you make it to the end?<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2230770/extras/434f133f01ce39b0edc9d081461a80ff.poster.avif?t=1726618775\" width=606 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2230770/extras/434f133f01ce39b0edc9d081461a80ff.webm?t=1726618775\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2230770/extras/434f133f01ce39b0edc9d081461a80ff.mp4?t=1726618775\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Unique builds and Ultimate skills for each character<br></li><li> Pet companions <br></li><li> Auto-aim or Manual aiming options<br></li><li> 3 maps and 5 characters available. Endless mode coming soon<br></li><li> Mini-bosses and End Level Bosses with unique behaviors<br></li><li> Short 25-minute play sessions</li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2230770/extras/4674caba443f01807c043c1945458735.avif?t=1726618775\" width=610 height=150 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Survive</h2>With different character classes, weapons, and companions, you must battle your way through various alien planets in an attempt to reach the final boss and win. Collect gems along the way to select new skills and upgrade your character.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2230770/extras/5b1f5620eff9d6c8a92d1dbd0d40549a.poster.avif?t=1726618775\" width=609 height=196 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2230770/extras/5b1f5620eff9d6c8a92d1dbd0d40549a.webm?t=1726618775\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Bosses</h2>Survive until the end of each stage and encounter the final Boss. <br>With an ever-changing set of skills, powers, and abilities, players must combine their efforts to take down the end-level Boss.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2230770/extras/a175c16e5559eaedddb1aec6c69dee9b.poster.avif?t=1726618775\" width=608 height=190 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2230770/extras/a175c16e5559eaedddb1aec6c69dee9b.webm?t=1726618775\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2230770/extras/a175c16e5559eaedddb1aec6c69dee9b.mp4?t=1726618775\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Ultimate Skills</h2>In addition to common skills, each character has unique skills and ultimate powers. You can combine these skills with common ones and build new, more powerful skills. Can you make it to the end?<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2230770/extras/434f133f01ce39b0edc9d081461a80ff.poster.avif?t=1726618775\" width=606 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2230770/extras/434f133f01ce39b0edc9d081461a80ff.webm?t=1726618775\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2230770/extras/434f133f01ce39b0edc9d081461a80ff.mp4?t=1726618775\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Unique builds and Ultimate skills for each character<br></li><li> Pet companions <br></li><li> Auto-aim or Manual aiming options<br></li><li> 3 maps and 5 characters available. Endless mode coming soon<br></li><li> Mini-bosses and End Level Bosses with unique behaviors<br></li><li> Short 25-minute play sessions</li></ul>",
